  <?dbhtml filename="xsetroot.html"?>

  <title>xsetroot-&xsetroot-version;</title>

  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction</title>

    <para>
      xsetroot is a tool for tailoring the appearance of the root window.
    </para>

